{"tid":734889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「轉倉」時被下令剝光豬蹲下答問題   和理非黃之鋒入稟索償1.6萬","createTime":"2018-07-09T04:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:20:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcc973769fdbffe0e8a98c0d1a67366687a32cc","tid":734889,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">河童鋒今日明白左膠套「大愛感化政權」係腦未呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180709/large/1531109938_3aa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180709%2Flarge%2F1531109938_3aa0.jpg&h=68de600f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒去年因公民廣場案被判入獄，期間「轉倉」往東頭懲教所時，遭懲教人員命令剝光豬蹲下再抬頭回答提問。黃之鋒認為懲教署做法濫權，入稟小額錢債審裁處就人身侵害及行政失當，追討合共1.6萬元。黃之鋒庭外表示，明白搜身有保安需要脫衣，但查問時也「衫都唔畀着」是不合理。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒帶同文件到西九龍法院，入稟前先接受傳媒訪問。他回應上周開記者會後，有人質疑搜身需脫衣是理所當然，黃回應稱，同意搜身時有保安需要，要求囚犯蹲下及脫衣，但他今次是針對查問時被要求脫衣、蹲下、抬頭答問的安排。<br />\n<br />\n質疑上訴委員會欠獨立性<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指，向懲教署索取職員口供時遭留難，加上處理投訴爭議的上訴委員會成員由懲教署署長委任，有自己人查自己人之嫌，認為長遠應考慮成立獨立的「監懲會」，避免黑箱作業。他指今次入稟法庭，有助直接索取口供，以及有公開盤問懲教署的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180709/large/1531109943_d9b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180709%2Flarge%2F1531109943_d9b8.jpg&h=fbf45c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本案申索人為黃之鋒，被告是代表所有政府部門處理訴訟的律政司司長。申索書指事發於2017年10月16日，過程約3分鐘，查問則關於個人、家庭背景及有沒有三合會聯繫，而懲教人員並無交待為何要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">裸體拷問</span></span>。案件排期於下月8日早上10時開庭提訊。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：SCTC28340/18】"},{"pid":"732b1f85edb50385011ec435b85651b6fd454ec0","tid":734889,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c74982e760527c26c0978055da4e14814b54ba","tid":734889,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"大愛感化政權  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0638fa1dbf2b0646ffab16dfbf3228fa065453d6","tid":734889,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"河童係一向唔著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37996d968ed2b2072573a47c7019afd0bb94f520","tid":734889,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b623a890fde60161dd705ab0b43a3f9a7b7fa133","tid":734889,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"佢唔係唔知唔work, 係佢認咗唔work就無得撈咋嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94304b220c97c95d87452a047e7fbeabc800e752","tid":734889,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b623a890fde60161dd705ab0b43a3f9a7b7fa133","tid":734889,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"佢唔係唔知唔work, 係佢認咗唔work就無得撈咋嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:03:54.000Z","msg":"但佢依家都無得參選立法會<br />\n<br />\n撈社運籌款"},{"pid":"3277e360cee1b4001830ed19148125fadbe3be12","tid":734889,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94304b220c97c95d87452a047e7fbeabc800e752","tid":734889,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b623a890fde60161dd705ab0b43a3f9a7b7fa133","tid":734889,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"c